headline.main: NATIONALIST GROUP IN SYRIAN CABINET; Coalition Seen for Working Out Complete Statute of Independence LEVANT FACES FOOD LACK Cereals Smuggled Out in War and This Year's Wheat Crop Is Below Normal

lead_paragraph: DAMASCUS, Syria, Sept. 21 -- Some of Syria's leading nationalist politicians, who were outstanding during two decades of negotiations for independence under republican France, have been included in the new Syrian Government that Prime Minister Hassan Bey Kakin announced late Saturday night.
abstract: new Syrian Govt seen working for complete independence
